     1. Developer says: "I need to add a method that calculates discounts."
     2. AI writes: tests/discount-service.test.js with a failing test.
     3. AI runs: node --test tests/discount-service.test.js → FAIL (expected).
     4. AI writes: src/domain/discount/service.js with minimum implementation.
     5. AI runs: node --test tests/discount-service.test.js → PASS.
     6. AI commits: test(discount): add discount calculation test + implementation -->
